from typing import List, Union
from accessor import getValue, setValue

def on_date_change(path: List[Union[str, int]], value):
    setValue(['date_value'], value)
    return

def on_time_change(path: List[Union[str, int]], value):
    setValue(['time_value'], value)
    return
    
def init():
    ### Get value of time
    time_value = getValue(['time'])
    setValue(['time_value'], time_value)

    return

init()
